text: Stinna Tange Kaastrup (born 13 July 1994) is a Danish para-equestrian. She and her horse Horsebo Smarties won two bronze medals at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1994 births Category:Danish dressage riders Category:Danish sportspeople Category:Living people Category:Paralympic equestrians Category:Paralympic bronze medalists
